headline.main: SOVIET UNITS YIELD; But Other Troops Gain With New Attack in Leningrad Region

lead_paragraph: KUIBYSHEV, Russia, Nov. 23 -- Russian troops have been pushed back in the central and southern sectors of the defense arc before Moscow, dispatches from the front acknowledged tonight.
abstract: USSR forces pushed back in central and southern sectors of Moscow line; USSR claims lines hold at Volokolamsk; Leningrad counter-attack reptd; bitter street fighting, Rostov
